<h3>What You Can Copy</h3>
<p>You do not need 425,000 pages. You need one repeatable content format that answers a real question. For a local business, that might be neighborhood guides. For a B2B company, that might be industry-specific use case pages. For an e-commerce brand, that might be product comparison pages.</p>
<p>The Flyhomes case study proves that <a href="/blog/ai-search-optimization-guide/">AI search optimization</a> and programmatic content can work when the content is genuinely useful. The pages were not thin. They contained real data, local insights, and editorial quality control.</p>
